    <date day="13" month="March" year="2017"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document specifies the extensions to the IS-IS routing protocol
   to carry and flood Flex Ethernet (FlexE) link state information.  The
   FlexE link state information is necessary for a device or a
   controller to compute a path that is required to over FlexE links.</t>
    </abstract>
